Data analyses. Distance analyses were performed with MEGA 6 (
Tamura et al . 2013
), utilizing a Neighbor- Joining algorithm (
Saitou & Nei 1987
) with the Kimura- 2 parameter model to estimate genetic distances (
Kimura 1980
). The robustness of nodes was evaluated through bootstrap re-analysis of 1000 pseudoreplicates.

Type locality: Macedonia , Holotype male, from the Peštera Momiček Cave, village of Belica, Mt. Dautica, FYROM ;
21 June 2002
, collected by S. B. Ćurčić, S. E. Makarov, V. T. Tomić, and B. M. Mitić. The type specimen is deposited in the collection of the Center of Biospeleology, Institute of Zoology, Faculty of Biology, University of Belgrade, 11000 Belgrade, Serbia .”.

